      "updated": 1717000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Editor reviews + edits in dashboard,\nclicks Approve → POST /publish.\n\npublishBlog() pushes drafts to every\ntarget. PUBLISH_MODE defaults to draft.\nDev log #n title prefix applied.",
      "fontSize": 11.5,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
